# LED Blink (ZedBoard)

## Overview
Basic LED blinking project for ZedBoard to verify board functionality.

## Board
ZedBoard (Zynq-7000)

## Tools
- Verilog
- Xilinx Vivado

## Description
Uses a clock divider to toggle an LED at a visible rate.

## Inputs
- Clock

## Outputs
- LED

## Notes
Serves as a basic test project for Zynq-based FPGA boards.
